definition.value: An amino acid opine resulting from the formal reductive condensation of the amino group of L-arginine with the keto group of 2-oxopentanedioic acid.
A tricarboxylic acid that is the 2-oxo derivative of homocitric acid.
A 17alpha-hydroxy steroid that is the 17alpha-hydroxy derivative of progesterone.
A benzoquinone resulting from the formal oxidation of catechol.
